    • all

      public List<ElementaryPattern> all()
      Description copied from interface: ElementaryPatternCatalogue
      Gives a list of all elementary patterns in this catalogue. The list should be constant and immutable (i.e., the very same list is returned each time all is invoked). The elementary patterns should be immutable, too.
      Specified by:
      all in interface ElementaryPatternCatalogue
      Returns:
      a constant list of all elementary patterns in this catalogue.

    • byType

      public Map<DiffType,​List<ElementaryPattern>> byType()
      Description copied from interface: ElementaryPatternCatalogue
      Returns a mapping from diff types to the elementary patterns that may match nodes of the given diff type. The returned map as well as all its values should be immutable and constant. *
      Specified by:
      byType in interface ElementaryPatternCatalogue
      Returns:
      A classification of elementary patterns by their diff types.
